{"id":535690,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/【立此存照】抵制肯德基甩锅时间线/","date":"2016-07-20T09:10:50Z","modified":"2016-08-11T02:24:35Z","title":"【立此存照】“抵制肯德基”甩锅时间线","content":"<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.13</span></h2>\n<p>中国社科院国家文化安全与意识形态建设研究中心副主任<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>朱继东</strong></span>在新浪微博用iPhone 6 Plus号召网民抵制肯德基和麦当劳（原微博已删）：</p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535691\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东.jpg\" alt=\"朱继东\" width=\"450\" height=\"620\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东.jpg 1565w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东-218x300.jpg 218w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东-768x1059.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/朱继东-743x1024.jpg 743w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></h3>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.14</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>共青团中央</strong></span>发表清华大学新闻学院教授、国际传播研究中心主任<a href=\"http://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309403997274060493474\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>李希光</strong></span>的文章</a>，称“资本集团渗透了几乎全部的网络媒体和有影响的传统主流媒体”：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535692\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团.jpg\" alt=\"资本渗透_共青团\" width=\"500\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团.jpg 1810w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团-300x249.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团-768x637.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/资本渗透_共青团-1024x850.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.16</span></h2>\n<p>线下出现大量号召民众前往肯德基示威的信息后，<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>共青团中央</strong></span>声称有“美粉公知”故意装成“极端爱国者”，给爱国主义抹黑：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535693\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅.jpg\" alt=\"共青团甩锅\" width=\"500\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅.jpg 1806w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅-298x300.jpg 298w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅-768x772.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅-1018x1024.jpg 1018w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.17</span></h2>\n<p>各地出现大量“爱国人士”在肯德基示威的图片／视频后，<strong><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">共青团中央</span>再次撇清关系</strong>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535694\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2.jpg\" alt=\"共青团甩锅2\" width=\"450\" height=\"558\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2.jpg 1806w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2-242x300.jpg 242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2-768x953.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团甩锅2-826x1024.jpg 826w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>人民日报海外版旗下的新媒体账号<strong>@</strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">侠客岛</span></strong></span> <a href=\"http://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309403998354773298121\" target=\"_blank\">发文</a>，<strong>称看了共青团中央转发的<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">李希光</span>文章后，“尴尬症都犯了”</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_535695\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-535695\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1.jpg\" alt=\"侠客岛1\" width=\"450\" height=\"90\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1.jpg 2150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1-300x60.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1-768x153.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛1-1024x204.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">截至发稿时，侠客岛微博文章阅读量已超已有136万；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_535696\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-535696\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2.jpg\" alt=\"侠客岛2\" width=\"500\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2.jpg 2182w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2-300x154.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2-768x394.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛2-1024x525.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">李希光本人无微博账号，该文微博首发@紫网在线 是一个平日转发仅两位数的账号。该文是经共青团中央转发才扩大影响的。</span></p></div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>共青团中央</strong></span>在微博暗示受到了误解、感到委屈：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535697\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈.jpg\" alt=\"共青团委屈\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈.jpg 2004w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈-300x207.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈-768x531.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/共青团委屈-1024x708.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.18</span></h2>\n<p>党报总编<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>胡锡进</strong></span>在微博称，<strong>拉横幅抵制肯德基的人是“一帮标准SB”</strong>，此微博后被删除：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535720\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进.jpg\" alt=\"胡锡进\" width=\"500\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进.jpg 1576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进-300x263.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进-768x674.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/胡锡进-1024x899.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.19</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\"><strong>人民日报</strong></span>发文批抵制行为：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535699\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报.jpg\" alt=\"人民日报\" width=\"500\" height=\"438\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报.jpg 1810w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报-300x263.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报-768x673.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/人民日报-1024x897.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">侠客岛</span>同时损了<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">朱继东</span>和<span style=\"color: #f04fb7;\">共青团中央</span></strong>（原微博已删）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535698\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅.jpg\" alt=\"侠客岛甩锅\" width=\"450\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅.jpg 1564w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅-203x300.jpg 203w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅-768x1137.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/侠客岛甩锅-692x1024.jpg 692w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>（本文将持续更新）</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[8635,9807,30806,31369,30038,9375,26878,8646,20162,9481,26089,25859]}